{"id":31714,"date":"2019-06-02T15:39:09","date_gmt":"2019-06-02T11:39:09","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=31714"},"modified":"2024-08-22T14:09:08","modified_gmt":"2024-08-22T10:09:08","slug":"dua-hamd-kathir-tayyib-mubarak","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/02\/dua-hamd-kathir-tayyib-mubarak\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Dua: Praise to Allah, abundant, good, blessed therein"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Anas reported: A man came and entered the row of prayer, breathing heavily. The man said, \u201cAll praise is due to Allah, abundant praise, goodness, and blessings therein.\u201d When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, finished the prayer, he said, \u201c<strong>Which one of you spoke these words?<\/strong>\u201d The people were silent, and the Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Which one of you spoke them? He said nothing wrong<\/strong>.\u201d The man said, \u201cI came and I was having trouble breathing, so I said them.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>I saw twelve angels competing for which of them would take it up.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 600<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Muslim<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u062c\u064f\u0644\u064b\u0627 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064e \u0641\u064e\u062f\u064e\u062e\u064e\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u064e\u0641\u0651\u064e \u0648\u064e\u0642\u064e\u062f\u0652 \u062d\u064e\u0641\u064e\u0632\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0641\u064e\u0633\u064f \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0645\u0652\u062f\u064f \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u062d\u064e\u0645\u0652\u062f\u064b\u0627 \u0643\u064e\u062b\u0650\u064a\u0631\u064b\u0627 \